parameter 40: The DVD edition of the pilot episode differs from the original broadcast and video editions: 1) The scene in which Sasha bursts in at August Octavius' funeral has been deleted. 2) The conclave meeting about Alexandra Serris' fate is now longer, featuring the primogens paying loyalty to Julian with a kiss to his hand and Julian warning Eddie that he will rip him apart if Eddie moves in on any other Kindred businesses. 3) At the very end of the episode, after Frank leaves Alexandra's with her locket, a new scene was added.  It cuts to San Francisco Bay, the camera dives underneath the waves to show Alexandra's body.  As the camera focuses in on Alexandra's face and her eyes open.  The scene cuts back to Alexandra's faded rose garden where one bush comes back to life and produces a gorgeous red rose.
